 <catch_line>DUTY TO REPORT DAMAGE.</catch_line>
 <order_by>8-2015</order_by>
 <text>
Every person who observes damage to a manhole or to any other part of the sanitary sewer system has a duty to report the damage to the Public Utilities Department. 
